data.description: Stunning waterfront  home in beautiful Green Cove Springs, Fl. Located high on the banks of Governors Creek. No Flood insurance required. Enjoy direct access to the St. Johns River  within minutes from your private dock. Spacious 4 bedroom, 3 bath with a Loft. Southern Yellow Pine Log Home built in 1993. The home was constructed with beautiful exposed beam rafters/collar ties, square cut logs, and frame/rough cut plank siding above the first floor and the converted garage area. The main home is appointed with tongue and groove pine walls and ceilings. The first floor consists of an open living, dining, and kitchen area with master  bedroom, a full bath, and a laundry room.
